data_table.description: Multiplexed Immunoassay Panel 7 (SABRe Project 2), Offspring Cohort Exam 7, Generation 3 Cohort Exam 1. This is the seventh in a series of immunoassay panels done on the same group of participants (Offspring Exam 7 and Gen 3 Exam 1). To get a full set of all the immunoassays done, please combine the following datasets: l_mpimn01_2005_m_0692s, l_mpimn02_2005_m_0693s, l_mpimn03_2005_m_0694s, l_mpimn04_2005_m_0757s, l_mpimn05_2005_m_0758s, l_mpimn06_2005_m_0792s, l_mpimn07_2005_m_0802s, and l_mpimn08_2005_m_0836s.

variable.name: apoa1
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for APOA1 is 22500000 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 113000000000 pg/mL. APOA1 values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use APOA1_I to see what records are below and above these limits. APOA1 values were set to unknown if APOA1_CV was greater than or equal to 24.8 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 26.5 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: apoa1_cv
